tags: parotta|nool parotta|thread parotta|lachha paratha|soft parotta recipe|kerala recipes|madurai parotta
description: Today, in our village, we cook a special thread parotta recipe. This parotta has different names in different places. In Karachi, it is called Lachha Paratha. In our place, we call it Nool Parotta. This Parotta has different layers: on the top, it's crunchy, and in the middle, it's very soft.Parotta lovers can try it at home. The taste is very delicious!

description: In this video we will see how to make brownie recipe in tamil. There are two types of brownies, cakey brownie which is dry and flaky and fudgy brownie which is softer and more chewy. Both brownies are different in their ratios of flour to fat content. For this recipe, we can use either chocolate bars or chocolate morsels. Also, in this recipe we have used egg but we can make an eggless version by substituting eggs with curd/yogurt.#brownie #brownierecipeintamil #brownierecipe Friends, please do try this brownie recipe at home and share it with your friends and family. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!Ingredients:150g semi sweet chocolate or dark chocolate50g Nuts or chocolate1/2 cup Butter (100g)3 Eggs1.5 cup Sugar (300g)1/4 cup Oil1 tsp Vanilla extract1 cup Maida (125 g)1/2 cup cocoa powder (40g)1/8 tsp Salt8 inch square baking pan 175c/350f for 28 min

description: Hey Guys ,Happy Navratri everyone , May this festive season brings lots of joy into your life like this video . Kaisi lagi video comments me btao also Guys to buy Mamaearth Thaali Hair Mask , Use Coupon Code : PAAYAL2024Mamaearth Link: https://bit.ly/3NgORszAmazon Link: https://amzn.to/3NfBFUWFlipkart Link: https://bit.ly/3Nj3PysNykaa Link: https://bit.ly/3Nk4srwThis Video is all about every indian and navratri . what people do on 9 days of navratri . Girls prepping for dandiya nights , buying lehenga choli for the festival season from jwala heri , janpat , gujrati lane , gk market , Sarojini nagar , getting blouse stitched by tailor , buying oxidised jewellery , dressing for the garba with friends and dancing our hearts out and bearing the feet pain after dancing whole night , soaking feet in hot water and salt . Indian aunty looking for girls and lokda for kanjak day . Indian bahu fasting and competing who will do better vrat and saas challenging bahu for do falhari . Sisters fasting on Navratri to loose weight as well as to worship and bribe mata rani to help them pass exams . Indian mom fasting , worshiping durga , cooking tasty vrat ka khana like kuttu ki pakodi , kuttu ke paratha , kuttu ki puri , sabudana khichi , sabudana tikki , samak chawal , samak khichdi , samak pulao , makana kheer , or just doing falahari for the whole middle class family and telling them to fast as well with mom and avoiding pyaaz for 9 days no cooking with onion  . Chintu chinki and savitri preparing for kanjak day  , kids choosing their kajak gifts before hand , mummy cooking bhog chole puri halwa for the kanya . Hoping Kanya will like the navratri gifts . Going out during Navratri shopping bartan , lunch boxes , waterbottle , kanjak gifts for girls and then eating navratri thali . Breaking fast by mistake , overeating during navratri vrat . Bhai behen april fools mom eating onion outside without telling indian mother . Craving gol gappe , indian street food , spicy indian food , chilly potato , samosa , chole bhature , momo , patisse only during the navratri fast and much moreThis video is filled with such memories and situations we all have been in. Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories.. You will have major nostalgiaDo share it with your friends and family especially mom ..
